    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, essentially indistinguishable from a new car. The exterior paint retains its original showroom luster with zero imperfections, scratches, or chips, and the body panels are perfectly aligned. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the upholstery shows no wear, and every electronic feature and accessory functions exactly as it did the day it left the factory. Mechanically, the car is flawless, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history and no performance issues. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in truly pristine, collector-grade condition.",
      "price": 49500.0,
